      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STRUCK GOLD (2) looks hard to beat again. Has won two of the last three, the latest this course and distance in slightly lesser grade. Drops in weight and expected to go close again. CONVINCEBILITY (3) returned from a spell with a strong run, finishing runner-up. Has a good second-up record and with brilliant early pace looks the one to run down. I'M A DREAMER (4) got the prize two runs ago at this track. Couldn't follow that up last time out when eighth over 1600m at this track, beaten 10 lengths. Well back in trip and can do better. PREDICTING (5) hit the frame two starts ago at this track but ran below par last time when sixth and beaten 5.5 lengths over 1300m at this track. Likely improver with top-three prospects. WOLFBURN (1) is fitter and can play a big role.",
